gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 133, Pelicans 89
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Pelicans, 133-89.  LeBron James led the way with 30 points (9-12 FG), eight assists and four 3PM for the Lakers, while Anthony Davis added 16 points and 15 rebounds in the victory.  Zion Williamson tallied 13 points for the Pelicans in the losing effort.  The Lakers improve to 14-9 on the season, while the Pelicans fall to 12-11.
